<mat-toolbar color="primary">
  <button mat-icon-button (click)="sidenav.toggle()">
    <mat-icon>menu</mat-icon>
  </button>
  Toolbar Title
</mat-toolbar>

<mat-sidenav-container #sidenav>
  <mat-sidenav mode="side">
    Sidenav content
  </mat-sidenav>
  <mat-sidenav-content>
    Main
  </mat-sidenav-content>
  <mat-sidenav-content>
    Events
  </mat-sidenav-content>
</mat-sidenav-container>
